room_title: Escape room "Capone" by Trapped Escape Game in Nashville
room_description: The year is 1937. Chicago is being run by the most notorious gang leaders history has ever known. Lawlessness rules the day as most of the police force is on the take. You have been falsely accused of being an informant to the FBI. Al Capone, the founder, and boss of the Chicago mob has had you captured and held in his apartment and is returning to settle the score in one hour. Nowâ€™s your only chance to escape before Scarface returns.
